data.description: Step into your new home and experience the epitome of comfort and charm! This delightful 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom ranch-style home boasts many updates, including a brand new roof (2024). Revel in the 2020 refinished hardwood floors, a modernized kitchen with stainless steel appliances and bathroom. The spacious family room is perfect for gatherings. With an unfinished basement awaiting your creative flair, the potential for personalization is endless. Nestled in a prime location with convenient access to highways restaurants and nearby parks, this home is move-in ready! Don't miss the opportunity to make this haven your own!
